import React, { Component } from 'react' export default class About extends Component { render() { return (
About Us

Who Am I?

A self-motivated and organised professional with more than 5.2 years of experience in web development and responsive designing using React js & Angular Js, who wants to be associated with an organisation that provides career development opportunities as a Frontend Developer and an environment to enable me to contribute to its growth. I am experienced in leveraging agile frameworks to provide a robust synopsis for high level overviews. Iterative approaches to corporate strategy foster collaborative thinking to further the overall value proposition.

I'm a seasoned front-end developer with a strong sense for aesthetics and interaction.

What I do?

Here are some of my expertise

Web Development

I have experience building websites and chrome extentions using JavaScript,React,HTML,CSS

Browser Developer Tools

As coming from the CS background, I have good grasp over fundamental concepts of DSA

SEO, PSO, Responsive Design

I am pursuing my internship with DevOps team at Juniper and working with tools like Jenkins, Docker, K8s
